Brik V. Eyre 
Executive Compensation
As Corporate Vice President, President, Hospital Products at BAXTER INTERNATIONAL INC, Brik V. Eyre  made $3,470,090 in total compensation.  Of this total $618,533 was received as a salary, $954,986 was received as a bonus, $985,634 was received in stock options, $831,958 was awarded as stock and $78,979 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


