Brik V. Eyre



Mr. Brik V. Eyre is Senior Vice President-Americas President at Baxter International, Inc. Mr. Eyre was previously employed as General Manager-U.S. Medication Delivery by Baxter Healthcare Corp. and President-Presource Products & Services by Cardinal Health, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from Utah State University and an MBA from The University of Tulsa.



